{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"35c4eefbd0","title":"在关于印度和尼泊尔联合声明的报道上的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"53f43676e5","index":0,"year":1959,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"35c4eefbd0"}],"tags":[{"id":"5bfa9ca15d","name":"宣言","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji42","name":"毛泽东全集第42卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/42-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji42":{"comments":[{"id":"de31b6edf6","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"35c4eefbd0","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指新华通讯社1959年6月16日编印的《参考资料》第二九三五期上登载的第一条新闻报道，题为《印新处报道印度和尼泊尔的联合声明》，介绍了印度总理和尼泊尔首相1959年6月14日在加德满都发表的联合声明的主要内容。"},{"id":"9d7d3addf5","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"35c4eefbd0","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"印度和尼泊尔的联合声明说到：“总理和首相还确信，为了和平的利益以及为了民族的和人类的进步，任何一个国家都不应该受到另一个国家的统治，殖民控制，不管什么形式，都应该结束。在这段话旁，毛泽东写了这条批语。"}],"contents":[{"id":"efea1284e8","type":"title","text":"在关于印度和尼泊尔联合声明的报道“上的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"35c4eefbd0"},{"id":"de31b6edf6","type":"paragraph","text":"尼泊尔不满印对它的控制，在这里，印度方面似已作出了一种让步，以便拉住尼泊尔。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"35c4eefbd0"}],"page":{"id":"f2ee9e4177","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"35c4eefbd0","start":149,"end":149}}}},"__N_SSG":true}